prompts.frontCover:
[ID: 3fa694ef-20e8-4893-8d6f-84cf38ee7efb]
A whimsical and funny dreamy fantasy greeting card illustration. A cartoon version of Jordan from the reference photo is skiing down a glistening, pastel-colored mountain made of frozen taro milk tea. He's wearing a vibrant ski jacket and beanie, looking back with a wide, excited grin. Instead of ski poles, he's comically holding two giant boba straws. A cartoon version of Lao Lao from the reference photo, wearing a cute, cozy ski outfit and her signature glasses, is expertly skiing beside him, laughing joyfully. She holds a single, oversized boba cup in one hand as if it's a trophy, with a cheerful expression. The "snow" kicks up behind them not as white powder, but as a magical spray of purple and pink sparkles and dark brown tapioca pearls. The sky is a dreamy twilight gradient of lavender and soft pink, with fluffy clouds shaped like spilled milk tea and a glowing full moon that looks like a giant lychee jelly. In the center, in a beautiful, readable, glowing white handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". Flat 2D artwork, ethereal lighting, crisp lines, magical atmosphere.
